section.section:
While it is effective, a milk processor permit authorizes the holder:
To collect raw milk;
To handle raw milk;
To process raw milk;
To pasteurize raw milk;
To store pasteurized milk;
To bottle or package pasteurized milk;
To prepare pasteurized milk for distribution; and
To distribute pasteurized milk.

text.section:
While it is effective, a receiving station permit authorizes the holder:
To collect raw milk;
To cool raw milk;
To process raw milk;
To store raw milk; and
To prepare raw milk for delivery to a milk plant.
